1. *Impresivno* je kako je taj mladi umetnik uspeo da napravi takvu revoluciju u umetnosti. (It is *impressive* how this young artist managed to make such a revolution in art.)
2. Videti Nijagarine vodopade uživo je *impresivno*. (Seeing the Niagara Falls live is *impressive*.)
3. Za mene je *impresivno* kako uspešno balansiraš posao i porodicu. (To me, it is *impressive* how successfully you balance work and family.)
4. Predstava koju smo sinoć gledali bila je *impresivna*. (*Impressive* was the show we watched last night.)
5. *Impresivni* su bili rezultati istraživanja koja su predstavljena na konferenciji. (*Impressive* were the results of the research presented at the conference.)
6. *Impresivnom* tehnologijom ova kompanija je uspela da smanji troškove proizvodnje. (With *impressive* technology, this company managed to reduce production costs.)
7. Ona je *impresivna* govornica, uvek uspe da zainteresuje publiku. (She is an *impressive* speaker, always manages to interest the audience.)
8. *Impresivno* je koliko dugo je ovaj koncert trajao, a da nismo ni primetili. (*Impressive* is how long this concert lasted, without us even noticing.)
9. Ovaj hotel ima *impresivne* pogled na more. (This hotel has *impressive* sea views.)
10. Kada sam video koliko je slika u tvojoj galeriji, bio sam *impresioniran* tvojim talentom. (When I saw how many paintings are in your gallery, I was *impressed* by your talent.)